\section{Results and discussion}
\label{sec:results}
We first present the results from the simultaneous unfolding of all observables with comparisons to the particle-level predictions from various simulations. 
Thereafter, we present results for the normalized, unfolded distributions of a subset of individual observables that demonstrate the highest statistical significance, to illustrate key observations from the measurements.
